---- MODULE CapabilityTokenPlusCal ----
\* Capability token lifecycle. Tokens are linear resources — granted once, checked N times, revoked exactly once.
\* PlusCal version — generated by tlaiser
\* https://github.com/hyperpolymath/tlaiser

EXTENDS Naturals, Sequences, TLC

CONSTANTS Ungranted, Active, Revoked

