\* ---- Temporal Properties ----
\* Property: GuardedWindowCannotClose (safety)
GuardedWindowCannotClose == []([][WindowGuard # Free => WindowLifecycle # Closed]_WindowLifecycle)

\* Property: RevokedTokenNeverChecked (safety)
RevokedTokenNeverChecked == []([][CapabilityToken = Revoked => UNCHANGED CapabilityToken]_CapabilityToken)

\* Property: WindowEventuallyRuns (liveness)
WindowEventuallyRuns == <>(<>(WindowLifecycle = Running))

